# Finding 096
- Severity: Low
- Pattern type: AI slop; Duplicate `applyMembersData` helper across members views
- File + line(s): `apps/jskit-value-app/src/views/workspace-settings/useWorkspaceSettingsView.js:219-225`, `apps/jskit-value-app/src/views/console/useConsoleMembersView.js:97-103`
- Why it can drift/fail: The same member list hydration logic is duplicated in two views. Any change to normalization rules must be applied to both.
- Concrete impact: Divergent members list behavior between workspace settings and console members screens.
- Exact remediation: Extract `applyMembersData` into a shared members view helper and reuse it.

